commentText: Keys User IDs, or more precisely user ID parts, used for determining the_public keys for encryption. If you just have one User ID, then you can_also use the method {@link #setKeyUserid(String)}. The User ID specified_in {@link #setKeyUserid(String)} and in this method will be merged_together and the public keys which have a User ID which contain a value_of the specified User IDs the will be used for the encryption. Be aware_that you may get several public keys even if you specify only one User_Id, because there can be several public keys which have a User ID which_contains the specified User ID.
